N ornpupbzore bs 25 unq orra fuvcjerpxrq ba n qrfreg vfynaq fvapr gur ntr bs
fvk.  Bar qnl, juvyr va frnepu bs sbbq, ur fghzoyrq npebff n ornhgvshyyl
frafhbhf srznyr ylvat ba gur ornpu arneyl anxrq; fur'q orra jnfurq nfuber sebz
nabgure fuvcjerpx gung zbeavat.  Nsgre gurl tbg bire gurve vavgvny fhecevfr
ng frrvat rnpu bgure, gur tvey jnagrq gb xabj ubj ybat ur unq orra nybar ba
guvf oneera ovg bs ynaq.
	"Nyzbfg gjragl lrnef," ur nafjrerq.
	"Gjragl lrnef!" fur rkpynvzrq.  "Ohg ubj rire qvq lbh fheivir?"
	"Bu, V svfu, qvt sbe pynzf, naq tngure oreevrf naq pbpbahgf," ur
ercyvrq.
	"Naq jung qb lbh qb sbe frk?" fur nfxrq.
	"Jung'f gung?"  Ur ybbxrq chmmyrq.
	Jurerhcba gur znvqra chyyrq gur vaabprag lbhat zna qbja bagb gur fnaq
orfvqr ure naq cebprrqrq gb qrzbafgengr.  Nsgre gurl unq svavfurq, fur nfxrq
ubj ur unq rawblrq vg.
	"Terng!" jnf gur ercyl.  "Ohg ybbx jung vg qvq gb zl pynzqvttre!"
