fnl lbh qb, lbh zhfg qb guvf sbe zr: tb gb zl qerffre naq trg zl tha.  Purpx
gb znxr fher gung vg'f ybnqrq.  Gura tb hcfgnvef naq fubbg obgu gung purngvat
gjb-gvzvat juber naq ure ybire.  Qvfcbfr bs gur tha, naq gura pbzr onpx gb
gur cubar naq gryy zr gung vg'f bire.  Qba'g jbeel -- V'yy cebgrpg lbh."
Gur zna urnef sbbgfgrcf, n qenjre orvat bcrarq, n pyvpx, zber sbbgfgrcf,
fvyrapr... naq gura gjb fubgf.  Zber sbbgfgrcf.  Svanyyl gur znvq pbzrf onpx
gb gur cubar naq fnlf "Vg'f qbar."
