N qehax jnf fvggvat ng gur raq bs gur one va n cbchyne fvatyr'f cynpr,
jngpuvat n lbhat, tbbq-ybbxvat zna jbexvat uvf jnl guebhtu gur jbzra.  Gur
thl qvqa'g nccrne gb or univat zhpu yhpx, naq ur jnf bayl fcraqvat n srj
zbzragf jvgu rnpu jbzna.  Nf ur jbexrq uvf jnl pybfre, juvyr ur pbhyqa'g
urne jung gur lbhat zna jnf fnlvat, ur ernyvmrq gung gur jbzra jrer fbzrjung
fubpxrq ng uvf nccebnpu.  Svanyyl, gur zna nccebnpurf n cerggl oeharggr naq
gurl uvg vg bss vzzrqvngryl.  Nsgre n ovg bs dhvrg pbairefngvba, fur unaqrq
gur lbhat zna ure ubgry xrl naq gurl fgnegrq bss sbe gur ryringbef.  Nf gurl
cnffrq gur qehax, ur fgbccrq gur yhpxl bar naq nfxrq uvz jung uvf zrgubq jnf.
